metadata.name: Stimulated Brain
metadata.description:
"Stimulated Brain" is a stunning piece of digital art that showcases a brain stimulated by electricity and otherworldly energy. The organ appears to beat with the rhythm of a living heart as it pulses with vibrant colors and intricate patterns. Mysterious wires wrap around and penetrate the cerebral matter, hinting at some unknown force powering this eerie yet captivating creation. Its beauty lies not just in its technical mastery but also in its ability to evoke feelings of fascination and wonder from anyone who gazes upon it. Overall, "Stimulated Brain" is a testament to the limitless potential of both human imagination and technological innovation, leaving viewers feeling inspired and awestruck.
Visuals & Audio by DrSKF. 2023. 
Perfect loop - 1080 x 1080
